                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="twelve columns"><a class="medium button" href="~/About/VitalDifference" id="learnmorebtn1" style="width: 125px;">Learn more</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="slide2">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="twelve columns">
                            <h1 style="text-align: center; float: right; margin-top: 10px;">We Pick Up and Deliver to Over 200<br />
                                Countries <span style="color: #f78f1e;">Around the World.</span></h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>
